Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.88,0:22:22.88,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:25.73,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.59,0:22:29.30,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說 妮娜好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:30.92,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs47\an9\blur2\bord2.5}我說 也幫我介紹一個貴族恩客吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:31.40,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs47\an9\blur2\bord2.5}啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.40,0:22:32.21,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs47\an9\blur2\bord2.5}我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.21,0:22:32.66,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs47\an9\blur2\bord2.5}啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:35.24,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs47\an9\blur2\bord2.5}可以的話 要比你還有錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:38.30,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不後悔嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:39.80,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.14,0:22:43.65,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在我回去的話 肯定就走不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:46.15,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.94,0:22:49.16,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在最後一刻也要你擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:52.57,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要跟約阿希姆走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:56.79,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很喜歡大夥以及露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:22:59.75,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可若跟你們待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.37,0:23:02.96,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總有一天又會憎恨起露加姐你來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.92,0:23:05.50,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而後便會憎恨自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.88,0:23:10.59,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只因為你的堅強 便會傷害到他人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:13.96,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只因為自己的軟弱 便會憎恨他人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.93,0:23:18.68,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想跟這個同樣軟弱 背負同樣罪孽之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.43,0:23:20.95,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}攜手同行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:23.90,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為跟他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.11,0:23:30.86,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺我們都會變得堅強和體貼一點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:33.88,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.91,0:23:37.99,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這孩子 真是讓人操盡了心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.89,0:00:04.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為何可以做到如此地步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:06.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在如此絶望的...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:09.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,任誰都只能尋找某種依賴的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:13.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為何他能理所當然地說出「要活下去」這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些東西見了太陽便會消失或者力量減弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:20.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,勝負關鍵在於能否撐到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:22.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要活下去!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:24.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為何這個男人的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:26.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是如此擲地有聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:28.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在我心中迴盪
Comment: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:11.98,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/--------START---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:13.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是折斷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:20.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,必須逃離這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:29.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:31.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:36.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:40.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託 我走不動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:53.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,千鈞一髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直跟瘋牛失控一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:00.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:01.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我在下面看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:06.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子艾倫他們都平安無事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:11.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 喂 沒時間傷感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:18.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:19.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:21.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但跑就不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:27.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,無論發生什麼事都不要露頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:32.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我會自己想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我一個人會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:39.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,絶對不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:44.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要露加姐姐陪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:47.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個桶藏不了兩個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,再說那樣的話誰來封蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:50.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:54.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是膽小如鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:04:00.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 倒不如讓人見識你是如何地貪生怕死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,屏住氣息不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:04.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,絶對不要弄出聲音來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:07.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定你這種貪生怕死之人 最能頑強地倖存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:12.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,完工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:23.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐 露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:35.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺自那天之後 自己就迷失在黑夜中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:37.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:41.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是太陽升起的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,終於到了拔此秘劍的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,僅此一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就比那個時候要好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:01.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 再怎麼燒也燒不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,源源不絶地湧過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:13.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,接招! 火焰爆裂丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:16.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:18.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,咦你妹啊 你個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,宰了你信不信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:22.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 這些都是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:26.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是此地死於瘟疫和拷問之人的怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:29.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,它們吸收被吞噬之人的意念後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,愈發龐大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,充滿了渴望得救的心願和怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:37.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,若心有怨念便變成這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:39.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,世間早已淹沒在痰盂中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:43.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為何只有阿爾比安發生這種怪事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:52.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,絶對不能有這種事情發生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:57.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,彷彿置身噩夢之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:02.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這真的是現實嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:18.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,若不想死 你自己也動動手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:20.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:25.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在這毛骨悚然的噩夢中站出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,並毫不退縮...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...唯一真實的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 背後也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞大人 請站在我背後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神...神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別祈禱!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣手就空不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:42.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你握著的是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:07:01.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 我要崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:07.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要死了要死了 我要死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了了 放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:10.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,放我離開這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟在這種時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,明明反正都要死...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:24.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:26.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,血還是熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,結局尚未可知啊 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:32.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,越是害怕 就越真切地感受到自己還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:37.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,越是吐血 便越是感受到那腔熱血
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,豁出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:41.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要求生 露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:45.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕 代表著求生的慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:05.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:34.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:37.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,生靈 亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:39.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,此地的所有靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正在呼喚同樣的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:49.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻 我的世界全體一條心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:52.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為我而鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:56.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為渴求我所創造的世界而鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:09:01.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一切皆化為同一個聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,它們在謳歌!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:11.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:18.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,它 它在和那個聲音共鳴!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:22.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:25.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個劇痛...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:53.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 光芒...四射
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格里菲斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:16.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在燃起熊熊火柱的...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:19.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...盲目群羊所聚集的聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:21.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天崩之時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:23.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他將降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:05.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一片慘象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塔和怪物都在一夜之間消失得無影無蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是不是在做夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我還活著...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:34.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,蓬蓬頭姐姐 原來你沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:37.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:40.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:43.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:46.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐...去找露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:48.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:51.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐...把我塞進桶裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:53.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,之後她怎麼樣我就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:56.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:57.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:59.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:02.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 在這瓦礫中怎麼找她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:04.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能死 露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:13.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏...我在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:14.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是在井下面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:20.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快拉我上去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:24.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快要凍僵了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:25.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:31.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚啊啊 好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:34.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:39.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:40.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...很暖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:43.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒白活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是庫夏人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會出現在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:00.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是上次那些斥候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,上次那個黑衣戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難道就是他?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:13.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 正如神諭所言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:15.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,此地發生了異變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:16.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他們也出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:20.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要找的人恐怕就在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:22.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,都走到了這一步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還活不下去就是老天騙人 大騙子!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:28.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,將這些人悉數拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:31.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,傷了他們一點也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:33.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是背著大劍那個男子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:34.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不必手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在砍下他手腳之前不可掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:45.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,死!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:46.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,送你歸西!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,個人感情暫且不論
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:50.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:54.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼比與你並肩作戰更振奮人心的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:57.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此 感覺是杯水車薪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:13:58.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你就吹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:01.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:03.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,敢動一下這些女人就...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:03.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:07.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟拿女人當人質
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是蠻夷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:13.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些異教徒 在我等聖地意欲何為
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:13.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾桑!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:15.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是倔脾氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:18.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞大人 您沒事真是萬幸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,副團長 你是怎麼脫險的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等下再詳談
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:26.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在我稍微離開期間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:28.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,事情變得有些微妙了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:33.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:37.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:38.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,又來?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:44.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔...魔獸?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:50.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...昨晚噩夢的延續嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:55.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在發生什麼我都不會吃驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:56.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,左德!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:57.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為何會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這...真是太駭人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:07.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別感慨了 要逃趕緊逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:10.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 全體別走散
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:12.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一口氣突圍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:40.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在那一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:44.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都屏住了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:46.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,目光不約而同聚於一處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格里...菲斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:05.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而後覺察到...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...追求的「希望」已降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:20.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,全軍 將他拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 施拉特大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:24.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別慌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:28.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個任務關乎我們巴基拉卡一族的復興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:34.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我族流放國外不下數百年的悲慘歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻正是千載良機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:39.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在大部隊到來之前拿下他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,上!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:50.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好極了 這邊人少了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:56.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個 在磨蹭啥呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:17.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫和劍士先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,難道還在那...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:22.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,站住 你還沒吃夠苦頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:24.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要你管 小嘍囉讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:25.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼?! 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:38.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,庫夏大部隊也來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:41.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他們沒發現我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:44.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎能這樣 你們要拋下他們兩個嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:46.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是迫不得已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:47.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這次真的會死人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,畜生!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:54.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他是何方神聖...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:18.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,非人之物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一而再再而三
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這次又是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:29.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他們沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:32.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 跟如此大軍為敵...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:36.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題 他肯定能保護好艾倫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:39.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 可別褂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:42.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會去討回你欠我的人情的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:44.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,傻逼 別嚷嚷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:55.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 除了我們還有人活下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:58.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,逃進塔的都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:02.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一溜煙地逃離塔的不信神者都活了下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:07.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想必他們再也不想祈禱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:09.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:14.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,求生和逃離恐懼是兩回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:16.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不隨波逐流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:19.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為了最終生還而掙扎求存之人才會倖存下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:24.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道神在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:30.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但還是為人類留下了自己想辦法解決的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:32.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐 那是?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這些花?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:36.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獻給死在蛋中的雛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:37.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:40.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒等孵出來就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不曾見過任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也不為人所知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有那麼一個寂寞的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:49.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沉眠在那瓦礫之下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想用這朵花為其餞別
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:55.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不管牠生前有著何等罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,至少死後不用孤零零的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:02.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 若牠的願望實現了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:05.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,今後 世界將會迎來怎樣的...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼有緣再會了 各位姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:11.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就此告辭 再見!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:13.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為了答謝你 我提供免費服務
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:18.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要趕路啊 先記著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是行色匆匆的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:23.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,總算鬆了口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:26.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道艾倫怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:29.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有那位黑色劍士保護 肯定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:32.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他對著摩茲古斯都毫無退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:37.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 保護一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:40.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,跟陪伴一個人大不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我去解下手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:46.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:47.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:52.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:57.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,約阿希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:20:59.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:04.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:09.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候我...覺得你...很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:13.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想著不去告發便會被你們殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:16.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然事到如今已難以敵口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:19.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,其實...我對你...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前很想和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:24.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我沒有勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,自己放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:28.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:31.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:32.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:33.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:42.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎...怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:46.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我...要追上黑色劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:47.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:50.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要棄僧籍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:54.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:59.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底沒能逃離童年陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:01.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然後它...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.86,0:22:05.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,終於成形 出現在我眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:11.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直像是那個懦弱的我命中註定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:14.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為立於黑暗中的唯一一人...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:18.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...黑色劍士所引領
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:43.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,從那天在邊境産生龜裂開始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.85,0:23:46.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的形態便開始崩潰
